A list of mephisto repositories can be found here:

http://macpro01.cct.lsu.edu/mephisto/repository/

You can use the --repository= option to list the
content of a certain repository:

perl mephisto.pl list --repository=0.2

and to force the installation of a certain repository
version:

perl mephisto.pl install â€“target-dir=/opt/saga/ --repository=0.2
